      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L I6, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated dual-VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp engagement, complemented by a documented subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The chassis retains factory-spec kinematics with fresh OEM bushings and Sachs dampers. Finished in Carbon Black with consistent paint depth and zero oxidation on the undercarriage, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
